LOCATION:Burbank Auditorium - Santa Rosa Campus
SUMMARY:SRJC Band & Choir: From Fortune to Fury (Show 2 of 2)
DESCRIPTION:SRJC Band &amp\; Choir presents FROM FURTUNE TO FURY feat. Ca
 rmina Burana!Only this concert also features saxophonist VINCENT HERRING.
   The SRJC Symphonic Band and Symphonic Chorus join forces for a one-of-a
 -kind concert with the electrifying power of Carl Orff's Carmina Burana! 
 Over 170 performers will take the stage for this epic collaboration and e
 xplore the full range of human emotion - from triumph and joy to fate and
  fury.  The program also features the SRJC Chamber Singers in five select
 ions\, along with the Symphonic Band performing the colorful Spanish paso
 doble Andr├®s Contrabandista and Ralph Vaughan Williams' radiant Flourish
  for Wind Band.  For tickets and more information\, visit: https://music.
 santarosa.edu/events (https://music.santarosa.edu/events)&#160\;
