 RTUNE TO FURY feat. Carmina Burana!<br /><strong>Only this concert also f
 eatures saxophonist VINCENT HERRING.</strong><br />  The SRJC Symphonic B
 and and Symphonic Chorus join forces for a one-of-a-kind concert with the
  electrifying power of Carl Orff's <em>Carmina Burana</em>! Over 170 perf
 ormers will take the stage for this epic collaboration and explore the fu
 ll range of human emotion - from triumph and joy to fate and fury.<br /> 
  The program also features the SRJC Chamber Singers in five selections\, 
 along with the Symphonic Band performing the colorful Spanish pasodoble <
 em>Andr├®s Contrabandista</em> and Ralph Vaughan Williams' radiant <em>Fl
 ourish for Wind Band</em>.</p><p>  For tickets and more information\, vis
 it: <a href="https://music.santarosa.edu/events" target="_blank" rel="noo
 pener">https://music.santarosa.edu/events</a>&#160\;</p>
