  for an evening filled with your favorite tunes from Wicked\, How to Trai
 n Your Dragon\, Gladiator\, The Little Mermaid\, Frozen\, The Lion King\,
  Moana\, Hercules and Beauty and the Beast. Whether you're a film buff or
  a theater lover\, this concert has something special for everyone. Don't
  miss out on this awesome live performanceŌĆöbring the whole family and e
 njoy this magical concert.  For tickets and more information\, visit: htt
 ps://music.santarosa.edu/events (https://music.santarosa.edu/events)
