LOCATION:Zoom
SUMMARY:Building Future as Immigrant Families (In Spanish/En espa├▒ol)
DESCRIPTION:California wants undocumented families to have bright futures
 \, and college is a great way to make that happen!  California believes i
 n us. All of us. Whether or not we have papers\, this state wants us lear
 ning\, growing and building skills that matter\, skills we can use\, with
  or without a Security Number.  &#160\;  SRJC Undocu ŌĆó Immigrant ŌĆó Dr
 eam Center invites you to join these virtual professional development ser
 ies designed for those who work with undocumented students.Register here!
  (https://events.zoom.us/ev/ApPBLph87f5_luSan-vCvSjbPLKtmvh1KgOjUdbd-bxlx
 iDLPMRt~AhrWN6KvTF36P9vCuV-ylaFaiNvrVDSaQ5-Do8DGVzZHuRCWff4dGVBn2g)  For 
 more information\, visit the SRJC Undocu ŌĆó Immigrant ŌĆó Dream Center W
 ebsite (https://dream.santarosa.edu/workshops-events-2025-2026)
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  California wants undocumented families 
 to have bright futures\, and college is a great way to make that happen!<
 /p><p>  California believes in us. All of us. Whether or not we have pape
 rs\, this state wants us learning\, growing and building skills that matt
 er\, skills we can use\, with or without a Security Number.</p><p>  &#160
 \;</p><p>  SRJC Undocu ŌĆó Immigrant ŌĆó Dream Center invites you to join
  these virtual professional development series designed for those who wor
 k with undocumented students.</p><p><a href="https://events.zoom.us/ev/Ap
 PBLph87f5_luSan-vCvSjbPLKtmvh1KgOjUdbd-bxlxiDLPMRt~AhrWN6KvTF36P9vCuV-yla
 FaiNvrVDSaQ5-Do8DGVzZHuRCWff4dGVBn2g" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Regi
 ster here!</a></p><p>  For more information\, visit the <a href="https://
 dream.santarosa.edu/workshops-events-2025-2026" target="_blank" rel="noop
 ener">SRJC Undocu ŌĆó Immigrant ŌĆó Dream Center Website</a></p>
