SUMMARY:The Environmental Forum - Fire and its Role on the Land
DESCRIPTION:The Environmental Forum is a series of presentations on a wid
 e range of environmental/climate change-related topics for students in co
 urse ENVST 40\, but all students\, staff\, and community members are welc
 ome. Presentations are free and open to the public - choose in-person or 
 on zoom.April1st "Fire and its Role on the Land\, LandPaths Good Fire pro
 gram"Lara O'Herlihy\, Senior Stewardship Field Specialist\, LandPaths  Fo
 r more information\, visit the Environmental Forum website! (https://ess.
 santarosa.edu/environmental-forum)
