 6 studying yoga and wellness in beautiful Costa Rica while earning 6 unit
 s of college credit.  The program includes yoga training\, cultural exper
 iences\, and exciting excursions such as visits to Manuel Antonio Nationa
 l Park\, Monteverde Cloud Forest\, and Indigenous communities.  For more 
 information\, visit SRJC's Study Abroad website! (https://study-abroad.sa
 ntarosa.edu/costa-rica-summer-2026-information)
