SUMMARY:Free Farmer's Market - Petaluma Campus
DESCRIPTION:The Free Farmer's Market is located outside\, under the outdo
 or canopy\, between buildings 400 &amp\; 500.  For faster check-in\, down
 load the "MySRJC App" and register with Redwood Empire Food Bank prior to
  the event.  Don't forget to bring your own grocery bags\, some will be p
 rovided on a first come first serve basis.  Can't make it? Leftover produ
 ce and other items are moved to the Welcome &amp\; Connect Center after e
 ach event.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  The Free Farmer's Market is located out
 side\, under the outdoor canopy\, between buildings 400 &amp\; 500.</p><p
 >  For faster check-in\, download the "MySRJC App" and register with Redw
 ood Empire Food Bank prior to the event.</p><p>  Don't forget to bring yo
 ur own grocery bags\, some will be provided on a first come first serve b
 asis.</p><p>  Can't make it? Leftover produce and other items are moved t
 o the Welcome &amp\; Connect Center after each event.</p>
